original:
Implant Y-7 is an enzyme booster that increases the Health, gained from foods and recovers additional Action Points per food item consumed.

Effects: Food restores +5 Health and +2 Action Points
Level: 1 / 2
translation:
植入体Y-7是一种催化酶，它能提高从食物中回复的HP值，并在每次摄入食物时获得额外AP点数。

效果: 食物HP恢复+5并且+2AP
等级:1/2

original:
Implant C-13 was originally designed as a defense turret subroutine to help eliminate Cazadores should they escape from their containment, but it's been repurposed for testing on human subjects. 

Effects: +20%%%% damage to Cazadores
Level: 2 / 2
translation:
植入体C-13原本是一个防御炮塔的子程序，用于帮助消灭逃逸的猎蜂。但它正被重新尝试用于人体。

效果：对猎蜂伤害增加20%
等级：2/2

original:
You gain a non-addictive subdermal Turbo injector. [Activated in the Pip-Boy inventory.]

Effects: Turbo for 3 seconds, 10 uses per day
Level: 2 / 2
translation:
你获得了一个不会上瘾的增压剂注射器。[在哔哔小子物品栏启用]

效果:增压效果3秒，每天10次
等级: 2 / 2

original:
Implant Y-7 is an enzyme booster that increases the Health, gained from foods and recovers additional Action Points per food item consumed.

Effects: Food restores +10 Health and +4 Action Points
Level: 2 / 2
translation:
植入体Y-7是一种催化酶，它能提高从食物中回复的HP值，并在每次摄入食物时获得额外AP点数。

original:
Implant Y-3 places an internal filtration system in the digestive tract that strips any liquid consumed of all radioactive particles before being processed by the body.

Effect: Immunity to irradiated liquids, 50%%%% of absorbed rads are converted into Action Points
Level: 2 / 2
translation:
植入体Y-3在消化系统中内置了一个过滤系统。它能在身体吸收前，将摄入液体所含的辐射粒子剥离。

效果: 免疫饮品辐射，将辐射量以50% 比例转化为AP
等级: 2 / 2

original:
You can be made... better... faster... stronger... Actually, just faster. The M-5 implant increases your crouched movement speed for greater efficiency as a test subject.

Effect: +40%%%% crouched movement speed
Level: 2 / 2
translation:
你会变得……更高……更快……更强……事实上，只是更快啦。植入体M-5可以使你的潜行的移动速度增加20%，让你作为实验体更有效率。

效果: +40% 潜行移动速度
等级: 2 / 2

original: This holotape contains an upgrade file for the Sink robotic assistant: "Auto-Doc."
translation: 这盘全息磁带记录着汇聚节点机械助手"自动医生"的升级文件

original: Implant Y-7 is an enzyme booster that increases the Health (HP) gained from foods and recovers additional Action Points (AP) per food item consumed.
translation: 植入体Y-7是一种酶加速器，它能提高从食物中回复的HP值，并在每次摄入食物时获得额外AP点数

original: Your spine has been replaced with advanced technologies: Your torso can no longer be crippled and your Strength (STR) and Damage Threshold (DT) have been increased (+1).
translation: 你的脊椎被替换成了更高科技的产物：你的躯干再也不会残疾了，而且你的力量和DT全都+1。

original: Your spine is back in your body, but some advance technologies remain: Your torso can now be crippled again, but your Strength (STR) and Damage Threshold (DT) bonuses have doubled! (+2)
translation: 你的脊椎又回来了，但一些先进技术留了下来：虽然你的躯干现在会残废，但你的力量和DT全都+2。

original: You can be made... better... faster... stronger... Actually, just faster. The M-5 implant increases your crouched movement speed by 20% (40%) for greater efficiency as a test subject.
translation: 你会变得……更高……更快……更强……事实上，只是更快啦。植入体M-5可以使你的潜行的移动速度增加20%/40%，让你作为实验体更有效率。

original: Implant Y-3 places an internal filtration system in the digestive tract that strips any liquid consumed of all radioactive particles before being processed by the body.
translation: 植入体Y-3在消化系统中内置了一个过滤系统。它能在身体吸收前，将摄入液体所含的辐射粒子剥离。

original: Implant C-13 was originally designed as a defense turret subroutine to help eliminate Cazadores should they escape from their containment, but it's been repurposed for testing on human subjects. (+10%/+20% damage to Cazadores)
translation: 植入体C-13原本是一个防御炮塔的子程序，用于帮助消灭逃逸的猎蜂。但它正被重新尝试用于人体。（对猎蜂伤害增加10%/20%）

original: Implant GRX is now available for surgical installation.

This prototype Auto-Doc is capable of performing a thorough physical exam and curing the patient of all common ailments - radiation sickness, lacerations, broken bones, even chemical addictions. In addition, it can also give haircuts and perform cosmetic surgery.
translation: 这个原型自助医生可以执行完整的身体检查，并且治疗所有的常见病痛，如辐射病，撕裂伤，骨折甚至化学上瘾。另外，它还可以理发和整容。

original: Perform surgery to install cybernetic implants?
translation: 是否执行手术来安装机械植入体？
